      "message": "1. Testing with Unit tests is not enough. Please test this with the Redfish Service validator, please refer to https://github.com/openbmc/bmcweb/blob/master/docs/TESTING.md and do actually setup subscription on a running instance and show what it sent.\n2. I doubt (99% sure) it\u0027s going to work in the way you expect. The way DBus subscription works is, BMCWeb listens for DBus events along with the LogService, so when a source service sends an event, both services receive it at the same time, and at this time, the LogEntry ID is not even assigned yet.",
