      "side": 1,
      "message": "This function is formatting common parts of the Event (https://redfish.dmtf.org/schemas/v1/Event.v1_4_0.json) and LogEntry (https://redfish.dmtf.org/schemas/v1/LogEntry.v1_21_0.json) both.\n\nwhat you are doing here is, you\u0027re going to store the URL under the LogEntry property of both Event and LogEntry structures, while only Event has it and the LogEntry has the \"@odata.id\" field on the top level and not under the LogEntry property that do not exist.",
      "revId": "07074a9af2da66c3f36cd5a9dd84b1524caf3bc6",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
